68    for layer in hidden_layers:
        h = hidden_states[layer]
        h_centered = recenter(h)
        self.H_train_means[layer] = torch.mean(torch.Tensor(h), axis=0).cpu().numpy()

        pca.fit(h_centered.cpu().numpy())
        directions[layer] = pca.components_
    return directions
